    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my car, and honestly, she\u2019s been such a reliable ride. It\u2019s in really wonderful shape\u2014super clean inside and out, and it still drives like a dream. It\u2019s perfect if you\u2019re looking for something well-loved and ready for many more miles of adventures. I\u2019d love for you to come by, take it for a spin, and see for yourself how great it feels on the road!",
      "price": 34500.0,
