      "timestep_posted": 48
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera 4S, a wide-body 996.2 featuring the iconic M96 3.6L flat-six engine with VarioCam Plus. This vehicle is mechanically sorted, having undergone a proactive IMS bearing retrofit and a recent cooling system overhaul including a high-flow water pump and low-temperature thermostat. The G96 6-speed manual transaxle shifts with precision, transferring power through the factory viscous-coupling all-wheel-drive system. The chassis retains its structural rigidity and features Bilstein B6 dampers that preserve the original suspension kinematics. While the exterior displays minor road-derived patina, the drivetrain is free of RMS leaks or bore scoring symptoms, making this an ideal candidate for a technical owner who prioritizes longitudinal and lateral performance over concours aesthetics.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 48
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used vehicle. Good condition. Well-maintained. Ready for immediate sale.",
      "price": 28500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 48
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between luxury and daily utility. The exterior retains its deep factory luster, showing only the expected minor stone chips on the front fascia consistent with careful highway use. The alloy wheels are free of major curb rash and are wrapped in tires with significant tread remaining. Inside, you\u2019ll find a smoke-free cabin featuring supple leather upholstery; while there is very light entry-wear on the driver\u2019s side bolster, the rest of the interior remains crisp and well-preserved. Every button, switch, and digital display operates exactly as intended, including the dual-zone climate control and premium sound system. Mechanically, this car is sound, having followed a strict preventative maintenance schedule throughout its life. We recently completed a full synthetic oil service and a multi-point inspection, confirming the brakes and suspension are in excellent working order. This is a reliable, turn-key example for a buyer looking for a high-quality driving experience without the brand-new price tag. Includes two sets of keys, all original manuals, and a clean title in hand.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 48
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting a distinguished example of automotive excellence, this vehicle has been curated to meet the needs of the discerning driver. It exhibits a refined aesthetic and robust mechanical performance, reflecting a history of diligent maintenance and care. The interior remains a sophisticated environment, while the powertrain delivers consistent, reliable performance across all conditions. This offering represents a premier opportunity to acquire a well-preserved asset that balances luxury with enduring value. Rigorously inspected and prepared for immediate delivery, it stands as a testament to our commitment to quality.",
      "price": 34900.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 48
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a reliable companion. It\u2019s in really solid shape, runs like a dream, and has been well-loved over the years. It's perfect for anyone looking for a dependable car that\u2019s ready for its next adventure! I\u2019ve priced it to move, so come take it for a spin and see for yourself\u2014you're going to love how it handles!",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
