      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 48
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This 996.2 Carrera features the robust 3.6L M96 flat-six paired with a precise G96 6-speed manual gearbox. Mechanically sorted with a documented LN Engineering IMS bearing retrofit and updated RMS. The chassis remains taut with refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers, ensuring the hydraulic steering rack provides the communicative feedback these cars are known for. Recent preventative maintenance includes new ignition coils and a high-flow water pump to optimize thermal management. While exhibiting honest patina consistent with its age, the drivetrain delivers linear power and a visceral exhaust note. A true driver-spec Porsche ready for immediate engagement.",
